</header>

<!-- HERO IMAGE -->
<div style="position:relative; overflow:hidden; height:240px;">
  <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512453979798-5ea266f8880c?w=1400&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Dubai real estate and property development aerial view" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" width="1400" height="240" style="width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; object-position:center 60%;" />
  <div style="position:absolute; inset:0; background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(0,104,117,0.15),rgba(0,37,59,0.25));"></div>
</div>

<!-- WHAT AEGIS BUILDS -->
<section id="what-we-build" class="section" aria-labelledby="build-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">What We Build</div>
      <h2 id="build-heading">AI Systems Built for Dubai Real Estate Agencies</h2>
      <p>Six specific systems we've deployed for agencies across the UAE — each integrated with your CRM, WhatsApp, and existing tools.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="apps-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-box"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#006875; font-size:24px;">chat</span></div>
        <h3 style="font-weight:700; font-size:1.0625rem; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">WhatsApp Lead AI</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Responds to every incoming lead in under 2 minutes, 24/7. Qualifies intent, collects property preferences, books viewings, and routes hot leads to agents — in Arabic and English.</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.8125rem; font-weight:600; color:#006875;">Leads contacted in 5 min are 9× more likely to convert (MIT)</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-box"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#006875; font-size:24px;">person_search</span></div>
        <h3 style="font-weight:700; font-size:1.0625rem; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">CRM Lead Scoring</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Ranks every lead in your CRM by likelihood to transact in the next 90 days — based on behavior, response speed, and inquiry patterns. Agents work the right leads, not the most recent ones.</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.8125rem; font-weight:600; color:#006875;">Integrated with HubSpot, Salesforce, Property Finder CRM, and custom systems</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-box"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#006875; font-size:24px;">description</span></div>
        <h3 style="font-weight:700; font-size:1.0625rem; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Document Processing AI</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Extracts and validates data from title deeds, NOCs, SPAs, tenancy contracts, and mortgage documents. Flags missing fields and RERA/DLD compliance issues automatically — what took days now takes hours.</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.8125rem; font-weight:600; color:#006875;">Trained on UAE real estate document formats including DLD and RERA templates</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-box"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#006875; font-size:24px;">smart_toy</span></div>
        <h3 style="font-weight:700; font-size:1.0625rem; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Property Listing Assistant</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">AI trained on your property portfolio answers buyer questions via your website and Bayut/Dubizzle listings — property details, availability, pricing, and viewing requests — in Arabic and English.</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.8125rem; font-weight:600; color:#006875;">Handles inquiries across web, WhatsApp, and property portals</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-box"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#006875; font-size:24px;">monitoring</span></div>
        <h3 style="font-weight:700; font-size:1.0625rem; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Market Intelligence Dashboard</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Aggregates DLD transaction data, REIDIN price indices, and competitive listing activity into a live dashboard your agents and management can act on daily. Know before your competitors do.</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.8125rem; font-weight:600; color:#006875;">Built on UAE data sources, not global benchmarks</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-box"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#006875; font-size:24px;">bolt</span></div>
        <h3 style="font-weight:700; font-size:1.0625rem; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Agent Workflow Automation</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Automates the manual tasks between viewings and closing — follow-up messages, document requests, listing updates, pipeline status syncs. Agents focus on relationships, not admin.</p>
        <p style="font-size:0.8125rem; font-weight:600; color:#006875;">Integrates with WhatsApp Business, Google Workspace, and your CRM</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:2.5rem;padding:2rem;background:#e7eeff;border-radius:20px;">
      <p style="color:#00253b;font-weight:700;font-size:1.0625rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Typical project timeline: 8–12 weeks · Covered by our 100% refund guarantee</p>
